: 525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 2.4520308630907084e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9567362513000984, \"rank\": 0.04522014092423281, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Marta's sixth Olympic appearance could end in heartbreak as she was sent off in her team's Group C clash against Spain at the Stade Matmut-Atlantique in Bordeaux.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7688555907844192, \"rank\": 0.30063436097252283, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\", \"score\": 0.9999999999508873, \"rank\": 4.901257884923525e-11, \"text\": \"Bordeaux\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Girondins_de_Bordeaux\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Challenging for a high ball on the edge of the Brazil box, Marta appeared to slightly slip and ended up clattering into a Spanish player with a 'really rash' high foot.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9567362513000984, \"rank\": 0.04522014092423281, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.598167017563129, \"rank\": 0.6571309579947835, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The referee immediately showed Marta a red card, leaving the Brazilian distraught and having to be consoled by her international team-mates.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Se o COI colocar a Marta no taekwondo \\u00c3\\u00a9 medalha certa pro BrasilOlha essa voadora kkkkkkkkkkkpic.twitter.com/PMLDhRfnUT  Marta was still in tears as she left the pitch and the Eurosport commentator admitted it was 'hard to watch' a legend of the women's game so crestfallen.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was rash from Marta, really rash,' the commentator said after watching a replay of the challenge.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Wow.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marta's last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is tragic.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her sixth and final Olympics and this is how she's going to go out.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She looks devastated.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": []}, {\